; Regression test for issue #1798: virtual transaction reporting incorrectly
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1798
;
; Virtual postings (enclosed in square brackets) should balance independently
; of real transactions. $1000 + $400 + $-1400 = $0 must balance without error.

2018/01/01 paycheck
	assets:banking:chequeing	$1900
	equity:company	$-1900

2018/01/02 paycheck
	[assets:budget:medical]	$1000
	[assets:budget:car]		$400
	[assets:banking:chequeing]	$-1400

test bal
               $1900  assets
                $500    banking:chequeing
               $1400    budget
                $400      car
               $1000      medical
              $-1900  equity:company
--------------------
                   0
end test
